{"name":"Limited Degree","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"9tg5myew4w9"}
{"name":"Activation","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","notes":"<p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-1}},"_id":"tz7t9jq9k09"}
{"name":"Instant Recovery","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"tv7ox9gvgmh"}
{"name":"Check Required","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"1vozrd0wxiw"}
{"name":"Concentration","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"9eockoppxp6"}
{"name":"Diminished Range","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the effect’s range increments by one step.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the effect’s range increments by one step.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"2e6312hc6ob"}
{"name":"Distracting","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Using a Distracting effect requires so much concentration or effort that you are vulnerable until the start of your next turn.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Using a Distracting effect requires so much concentration or effort that you are vulnerable until the start of your next turn.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"2keeijl36we"}
{"name":"Grab-Based","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An attack with this flaw requires you to successfully grab and hold a target before the effect can be used.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An attack with this flaw requires you to successfully grab and hold a target before the effect can be used.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"73e4ybdtyh4"}
{"name":"Increased Action","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw increases the action required to use an effect by one step (Free to Move, Move to Standard, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Each rank of this flaw increases the action required to use an effect by one step (Free to Move, Move to Standard, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"iswoducn9pi"}
{"name":"Limited","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An effect with this flaw only works under certain circumstances, or has a significant restriction on its use.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw only works under certain circumstances, or has a significant restriction on its use.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"9w64m2baa8q"}
{"name":"Noticeable","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>A continuous or permanent effect with this flaw is very noticeable (glows, makes a loud noise, etc.).</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","notes":"<p>A continuous or permanent effect with this flaw is very noticeable (glows, makes a loud noise, etc.).</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-1}},"_id":"iipcsh0z4up"}
{"name":"Quirk","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>A Quirk is a minor flaw, often something specific to a character or power, that doesn’t quite rise to the level of a full -1 cost per rank flaw.</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","notes":"<p>A Quirk is a minor flaw, often something specific to a character or power, that doesn’t quite rise to the level of a full -1 cost per rank flaw.</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-1}},"_id":"t8m1fvjqlo"}
{"name":"Reduced Range","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the range of an effect (Ranged to Close, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the range of an effect (Ranged to Close, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"b77z04cpsdn"}
{"name":"Resistible","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An effect with this flaw allows an additional resistance check, or is resisted by a different defense than usual.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw allows an additional resistance check, or is resisted by a different defense than usual.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"nau3dog8ig"}
{"name":"Sense-Dependent","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>The target must be able to perceive the effect with a particular sense for it to work.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>The target must be able to perceive the effect with a particular sense for it to work.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"03e4jimtkzj"}
{"name":"Side Effect","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>If you fail to use the effect properly, or even if you succeed, you suffer a negative side effect.</p><p>–1 or –2 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>If you fail to use the effect properly, or even if you succeed, you suffer a negative side effect.</p><p>–1 or –2 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"ow1lzojjz0q"}
{"name":"Tiring","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Using the effect is physically or mentally taxing, causing you to become fatigued.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Using the effect is physically or mentally taxing, causing you to become fatigued.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"7328xm4zjh9"}
{"name":"Uncontrolled","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have no control over when the effect activates or what it does; the GM decides.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>You have no control over when the effect activates or what it does; the GM decides.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"deq2n888y0r"}
{"name":"Unreliable","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An Unreliable effect only works some of the time (5 uses, or requires a check each time).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An Unreliable effect only works some of the time (5 uses, or requires a check each time).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"xgutrz6zycc"}
{"name":"Feedback","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You suffer damage when a manifestation of your effect is damaged.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>You suffer damage when a manifestation of your effect is damaged.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"4nem7txreep"}
{"name":"Inaccurate","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An effect with this flaw is hard to control or wildly inaccurate. Each rank gives you a –2 penalty to attack checks.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw is hard to control or wildly inaccurate. Each rank gives you a –2 penalty to attack checks.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"b64837gg43"}
{"name":"Permanent","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>A continuous effect with this flaw becomes permanent in duration. It cannot be turned off and cannot be improved using extra effort.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>A continuous effect with this flaw becomes permanent in duration. It cannot be turned off and cannot be improved using extra effort.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"z2fjumkk6e"}
{"name":"Removable","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Removable applies to the power as a whole. The flaw is worth –1 point per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -1 point per 5 points.</p>","notes":"<p>Removable applies to the power as a whole. The flaw is worth –1 point per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -1 point per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-1}},"_id":"gdmqfl1dsn"}
{"name":"Easily Removable","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","notes":"<p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-2}},"_id":"i1c7kg3ae7q"}